mysql++: mysql++ (A C++ wrapper for the MySQL C API)
mysql++:
mysql++: MySQL++ is a C++ wrapper for the MySQLs C API.
mysql++: It is built around the same principles as the Standard C++ Library,
mysql++: to make dealing with the database as easy as dealing with STL
mysql++: containers. In addition, MySQL++ provides facilities that let you
mysql++: avoid the most repetitive sorts of SQL within your own code,
mysql++: providing native C++ interfaces for these common tasks.
mysql++:
mysql++: Homepage: http://tangentsoft.net/mysql++/
